{"tid":1955961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】河南郟縣「二度封城」 3醫生被驗出是「隱形病人」致53人隔離","createTime":"2020-04-03T00:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T02:46:42.000Z","uid":12558,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a046af4d78910f5e0edee3ad81605a0c6a1e78fd","tid":1955961,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:14:02.000Z","msg":"河南省郟縣人民醫院3名醫生被檢測為「無症狀感染者」，郟縣防疫辦公室昨天（1日）宣佈全縣再度封村、封小區（社區），所有人員憑證出入，除超市、醫院、市場外的商店一律停業。<br />\n<br />\n郟縣此舉被認為是「二度封城」，昨晚引起關注。據《南華早報》報道，猶如宵禁等級的封鎖，已於3月31日起實施。而同在3月31日，河南省官方已要求加強無症感染者管理。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，郟縣交通運輸局一名官員確認了全縣進入封閉狀態。他說，「這時候最好不要進出郟縣，沒有人能夠進出」。<br />\n<br />\n當地一名23歲的王小姐表示，她是在前天（31日）下午被村裡通知這項封鎖令。官方要求民眾購買日用品及蔬菜，為封城作準備。而她很擔心疫情的新發展，因為郟縣人民醫院離自己家只有約2公里。<br />\n<br />\n根據內地媒體報道，事件起因是一名河南省漯河市的王姓女清潔人員，曾於3月21日搭乘長途客運前往郟縣，由一名郟縣人民醫院的張姓醫生駕車搭載前往掃墓，兩人並一同用餐3次。事後，王女在28日確診為武漢肺炎病例。<br />\n<br />\n再經追查發現，張姓醫生早在3月13日晚間，與同院的劉姓、周姓醫生在飯店同桌用餐。其中，劉姓醫生曾有武漢旅遊史，回郟縣後即自行隔離14天，用餐時已隔離期滿。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，郟縣人民醫院25日對參與防疫的一線醫護人員進行體檢，在核酸篩查中發現張、周二名醫生是「無症狀感染者」。至於劉姓醫生的核酸檢測為「陽性、無症狀」。目前這3名醫生正接受集中隔離醫學觀察。<br />\n<br />\n此外，官方已追蹤到與王女密切接觸者15人，與劉、張、周3名醫生密切接觸者53人，均接受集中隔離醫學觀察中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200402/X6GJJLPOUIKXNXDTBI4NRDAFSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200402%2FX6GJJLPOUIKXNXDTBI4NRDAFSM%2F&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMrTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=f9ab7f88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200402%2FX6GJJLPOUIKXNXDTBI4NRDAFSM%2F&h=08aa5ffd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200402/X6GJJLPOUIKXNXDTBI4NRDAFSM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c453a33482b19d851ca8c8c78832f7d948e590f6","tid":1955961,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:15:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addb2bd7967e54f75b04a3647447ac26d573ad56","tid":1955961,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229e3f54a57d1ac0de8e58cfd89f8a91d3d79bd3","tid":1955961,"uid":74622,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T01:02:17.000Z","msg":"陽性無病徵 唔計數啦"},{"pid":"658ca49063f18f176060ec1c85cba0de67ec1891","tid":1955961,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T01:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b11f8252e3e16582865b5cbd9fae227b7fa8b5f","tid":1955961,"uid":186388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T01:20:19.000Z","msg":"大陸啲人未必咁注意衛生，可能唔小心摸咗眼耳口鼻中招，然後記得同乜乜食過飯，就屈人話人傳染你。"},{"pid":"7fc7fa87833c2267f5ae771ab8d8507444796867","tid":1955961,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T01:21:39.000Z","msg":"變形俠醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b48bcfebbf31179c27dc95ac0cc69162a19d485","tid":1955961,"uid":189499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T01:28:08.000Z","msg":"聽唔到  睇唔到 唔好話我知"},{"pid":"ba7151be3efb09399af5a2df7c8ee304ad92cd4b","tid":1955961,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03